<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>NextSelf</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #09090b;
      --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, .08);
      --text: #text;
      --muted: #b4b4b8;
      --accent: #5b8cff;
      --accent2: #8b5cf6
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: #fff;
      overflow-x: hidden
    }

    .orb,
    .orb2 {
      position: fixed;
      border-radius: 50%;
      filter: blur(120px);
      z-index: -1
    }

    .orb {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      background: #355cff44;
      top: 0;
      left: -50px
    }

    .orb2 {
      width: 350px;
      height: 350px;
      background: #8b5cf644;
      right: -50px;
      top: 200px
    }

    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, .5);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
      padding: 18px 8%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      z-index: 100
    }

    nav a {
      color: #ddd;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    section {
      padding: 90px 8%
    }

    .hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 90vh
    }

    .badge,
    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--card);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .05);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
      margin: 18px 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, #b4b4b8);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 650px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .glass {
      background: var(--card);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .1);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(91, 140, 255, .15)
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px
    }

    .card {
      transition: .3s;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      border-color: rgba(91, 140, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .app {
      border: 1px solid rgba(91, 140, 255, .4);
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(91, 140, 255, .2);
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    input,
    textarea,
    select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 14px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      background: #111;
      border: 1px solid #333;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-family: inherit;
    }

    input:focus,
    textarea:focus,
    select:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #5b8cff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(91, 140, 255, .4)
    }

    .chat {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .chat .bubble {
      padding: 14px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      max-width: 75%;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .user {
      background: #1c1c1f;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      margin-left: auto;
      border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
    }

    .ai {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
    }

    .hack {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(91, 140, 255, .12), rgba(139, 92, 246, .12));
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 40px;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: .7s
    }

    .reveal.show {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: none
    }

    #toast {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      background: #18181b;
      border: 1px solid #27272a;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: none;
      z-index: 1000;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      animation: slideUp 0.3s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      from {
        transform: translateY(100px);
        opacity: 0;
      }

      to {
        transform: none;
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @media(max-width:900px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="orb"></div>
  <div class="orb2"></div>
  <nav><strong>NextSelf</strong>
    <div><a href="#how">How it works</a><a href="#create">Create</a><a href="#chat">Chat</a><a href="#hack">AI Hack</a>
    </div>
    <button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('create').scrollIntoView()">Start Now</button>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero reveal">
    <div><span class="badge">Built in Founder Labs</span>
      <h1>Meet the version of you who already made it.</h1>
      <p class="sub">NextSelf helps you reflect, plan, and receive advice from the person you are becoming. Speak
        directly to your successful NextSelf.</p>
      <br><button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('create').scrollIntoView()">Create My NextSelf</button>
    </div>
    <div class="glass">
      <h3>Message from NextSelf</h3><br>
      <p style="font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; color: #e4e4e7;">"You are closer than you think. But your current
        habits need to match your future identity. Stop negotiating with your dreams."</p>
      <br><small style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500;">NextSelf generated • 4 seconds ago</small>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="how" class="reveal">
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="glass card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px;">Your Goals</h3>
        <p class="sub">Tell NextSelf what you are desperately trying to build or achieve in the next year.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass card">
        <h3 style="color: var(--accent2); margin-bottom: 8px;">Your Fears</h3>
        <p class="sub">Be deeply honest about what is holding you back. Absolute honesty unlocks the best guidance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="glass card">
        <h3 style="color: #34d399; margin-bottom: 8px;">Your Next Moves</h3>
        <p class="sub">Receive a crystal clear letter, critical warnings, tactical habits, and a customized daily
          mantra.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="create" class="reveal">
    <div class="glass app">
      <h2>Create Your NextSelf</h2><br>
      <p class="sub">Be deeply honest. NextSelf responds to absolute truth, not performance.</p><br>

      <input id="name" placeholder="Your name">
      <input id="age" placeholder="Current age" type="number" min="1" max="120">
      <input id="goal" placeholder="Core goal / Dream (e.g. build a profitable AI company)">
      <textarea id="struggle" placeholder="What are you struggling with right now? Be brutally honest."
        rows="4"></textarea>
      <input id="year" placeholder="Where do you want to be in 1 year? (e.g. running my own venture)">
      <select id="tone">
        <option>Motivational</option>
        <option>Brutally Honest</option>
        <option>Calm Mentor</option>
        <option>CEO Mode</option>
      </select>
      <div id="error" style="color:#ff8a8a; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 10px;"></div><br>
      <button class="btn" style="width: 100%; padding: 16px;" onclick="generate()">Generate My NextSelf</button>
      <div id="result"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="chat" class="chat reveal">
    <h2>Ask your NextSelf anything.</h2><br>
    <div id="chat-messages"
      style="max-height: 450px; overflow-y: auto; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-bottom: 10px;">
      <div class="bubble user">
        <strong>You:</strong><br>
        Will I actually make it?
      </div>
      <div class="bubble ai">
        <strong>NextSelf:</strong><br>
        Only if your daily actions stop negotiating with your dreams.
      </div>
      <div class="bubble user">
        <strong>You:</strong><br>
        What should I focus on this week?
      </div>
      <div class="bubble ai">
        <strong>NextSelf:</strong><br>
        Remove distractions. Build one visible proof of progress. Then show it to the world.
      </div>
      <div id="chat-loading"
        style="display:none; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 10px;">NextSelf is
        thinking...</div>
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">
      <input id="chat-question" placeholder="Ask your NextSelf a follow-up question..." style="margin: 0; flex: 1;"
        onkeydown="if(event.key === 'Enter') { event.preventDefault(); sendChat(); }">
      <button class="btn" onclick="sendChat()" style="white-space: nowrap; margin: 0; padding: 12px 24px;">Ask
        NextSelf</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="hack" class="glass hack reveal" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px;">
    <h2 style="color: var(--accent2);">AI Hack: Premium Prompt Generator</h2><br>
    <p class="sub">Generate an engineered, high-converting prompt to reverse-engineer any dream role. Copy it directly
      into ChatGPT/Gemini to get a hyper-detailed 4-week execution plan.</p><br>

    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; text-align: left;">
      <div>
        <label style="font-weight: 600; color: #fff; font-size: 0.95rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;">Enter Your
          Dream Role / Goal:</label>
        <input id="hack-role" placeholder="e.g. YC Founder, AI Solopreneur, Lead Product Designer" style="margin: 0;">
      </div>

      <div>
        <label style="font-weight: 600; color: #fff; font-size: 0.95rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 5px;">Mentor
          Persona Tone:</label>
        <select id="hack-tone" style="margin: 0;">
          <option value="Elite No-Nonsense Mentor">Elite No-Nonsense Mentor</option>
          <option value="Socratic Coach">Socratic Coach</option>
          <option value="Silicon Valley VC">Silicon Valley VC</option>
          <option value="Stoic Philosopher">Stoic Philosopher</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <button class="btn" onclick="generateHackPrompt()"
        style="padding: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 10px; width: 100%;">
        Generate Engineered Prompt
      </button>

      <div id="hack-output-container" style="display: none; margin-top: 20px;">
        <h4 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px;">Your Engineered Prompt:</h4>
        <div style="position: relative;">
          <textarea id="hack-prompt-text" readonly rows="12"
            style="background: #09090b; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #a1a1aa; padding: 20px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; resize: none; border-radius: 14px; width: 100%; padding-right: 80px;"></textarea>
          <button class="btn" onclick="copyHackPrompt()"
            style="position: absolute; top: 10px; right: 10px; padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 0.8rem; background: var(--accent2);">
            Copy
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="reveal" style="text-align:center">
    <h2>You did not just build a page. You built a mirror.</h2><br>
    <p class="sub" style="margin:auto">NextSelf turns AI from a tool into a personal growth experience.</p><br>
    <button class="btn" onclick="toast()">Share My NextSelf</button>
  </section>

  <footer>Founder Labs • NextSelf Live Build</footer>
  <div id="toast">Your NextSelf moment is ready to share.</div>

  <script>
    // Determine API Base URL dynamically to support local Live Server (port 5500) and file:// protocol
    const API_BASE = window.location.port !== '5000' ? 'http://localhost:5000' : '';

    // Track the active user profile and chat history
    let activeProfile = null;
    let chatHistory = [
      { role: 'user', message: "Will I actually make it?" },
      { role: 'assistant', message: "Only if your daily actions stop negotiating with your dreams." },
      { role: 'user', message: "What should I focus on this week?" },
      { role: 'assistant', message: "Remove distractions. Build one visible proof of progress. Then show it to the world." }
    ];

    async function generate() {
      const n = document.getElementById('name').value.trim();
      const a = document.getElementById('age').value.trim();
      const g = document.getElementById('goal').value.trim();
      const s = document.getElementById('struggle').value.trim();
      const y = document.getElementById('year').value.trim();
      const t = document.getElementById('tone').value;
      const errorDiv = document.getElementById('error');
      const resultDiv = document.getElementById('result');

      // Correct check: check all inputs exist and are not empty
      if (!n || !a || !g || !s || !y || !t) {
        errorDiv.innerText = 'Please fill all required fields.';
        return;
      }
      errorDiv.innerText = '';
      resultDiv.innerHTML = '<p style="margin-top:20px; color: var(--accent); font-style: italic; font-weight: 500;">Establishing secure connection to the future self...</p>';

      activeProfile = { name: n, age: a, goal: g, struggle: s, oneYearVision: y, tone: t };

      try {
        const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/generate-NextSelf`, {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify(activeProfile)
        });
        const resData = await response.json();
        if (!resData.success) {
          throw new Error(resData.error || 'Failed to transmit message.');
        }

        const data = resData.data;
        resultDiv.innerHTML = `
          <div class="glass reveal show" style="margin-top:30px; border: 1px solid rgba(91, 140, 255, 0.4); box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(91, 140, 255, 0.15);">
            <h3 style="color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700;">Transmission Received</h3><br>
            <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.6; font-style: italic; color: #f4f4f5; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); padding: 20px; border-radius: 14px; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px;">"${data.message}"</p>
            
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent2); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Future Identity</h4>
            <p style="color: #e4e4e7; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">${data.futureIdentity}</p>
            
            <h4 style="color: #fb7185; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Future Warning</h4>
            <p style="color: #e4e4e7; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">${data.warning}</p>
            
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Tactical Next Moves</h4>
            <ol style="margin-left: 20px; color: #e4e4e7; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 15px;">
              ${data.nextMoves.map(move => `<li>${move}</li>`).join('')}
            </ol>
            
            <h4 style="color: #34d399; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Daily Habit to Start Today</h4>
            <p style="color: #e4e4e7; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 15px;">${data.habit}</p>

            <h4 style="color: #fbbf24; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Daily Mantra</h4>
            <p style="color: #fef08a; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem;">"${data.mantra}"</p>
          </div>
        `;

        // Set up the follow-up chat
        chatHistory = [
          { role: 'assistant', message: data.message }
        ];
        renderChat();
        document.getElementById('chat').scrollIntoView();

      } catch (err) {
        console.error(err);
        errorDiv.innerText = err.message || 'NextSelf could not respond right now. Please try again.';
        resultDiv.innerHTML = '';
      }
    }

    function renderChat() {
      const chatSection = document.getElementById('chat');
      chatSection.innerHTML = `
        <h2>Ask your NextSelf anything.</h2><br>
        <div id="chat-messages" style="max-height: 450px; overflow-y: auto; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-right: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); padding-bottom: 10px;">
          ${chatHistory.map(chat => `
            <div class="bubble ${chat.role === 'user' ? 'user' : 'ai'}">
              <strong>${chat.role === 'user' ? 'You' : 'NextSelf'}:</strong><br>
              ${chat.message}
            </div>
          `).join('')}
          <div id="chat-loading" style="display:none; color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 10px;">NextSelf is thinking...</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-top: 15px;">
          <input id="chat-question" placeholder="Ask your NextSelf a follow-up question..." style="margin: 0; flex: 1;" onkeydown="if(event.key === 'Enter') { event.preventDefault(); sendChat(); }">
          <button class="btn" onclick="sendChat()" style="white-space: nowrap; margin: 0; padding: 12px 24px;">Ask NextSelf</button>
        </div>
      `;
      // Scroll chat to bottom
      const messagesDiv = document.getElementById('chat-messages');
      if (messagesDiv) {
        messagesDiv.scrollTop = messagesDiv.scrollHeight;
      }
    }

    async function sendChat() {
      const questionInput = document.getElementById('chat-question');
      const question = questionInput.value.trim();
      if (!question) return;

      // Fallback profile if they haven't generated a reflection yet
      if (!activeProfile) {
        activeProfile = {
          name: "Seeker",
          age: "25",
          goal: "Build a meaningful life and career",
          struggle: "Distraction and lack of consistency",
          oneYearVision: "Becoming highly disciplined and successful",
          tone: "Motivational"
        };
      }

      questionInput.value = '';
      chatHistory.push({ role: 'user', message: question });
      renderChat();

      const loadingIndicator = document.getElementById('chat-loading');
      if (loadingIndicator) loadingIndicator.style.display = 'block';

      try {
        const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/api/chat-NextSelf`, {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify({
            userProfile: activeProfile,
            chatHistory: chatHistory.slice(0, -1).map(c => ({ role: c.role, message: c.message })),
            question: question
          })
        });
        const resData = await response.json();
        if (!resData.success) {
          throw new Error(resData.error || 'Failed to communicate with future self.');
        }
        chatHistory.push({ role: 'assistant', message: resData.reply });
        renderChat();
      } catch (err) {
        console.error(err);
        chatHistory.push({ role: 'assistant', message: `I lost the transmission link: ${err.message}` });
        renderChat();
      }
    }

    function generateHackPrompt() {
      const role = document.getElementById('hack-role').value.trim();
      const tone = document.getElementById('hack-tone').value;
      const outputContainer = document.getElementById('hack-output-container');
      const promptTextArea = document.getElementById('hack-prompt-text');

      if (!role) {
        alert('Please enter a dream role.');
        return;
      }

      const prompt = `You are a world-class strategic growth advisor acting as a ${tone}. Reverse-engineer a detailed, highly practical execution plan for someone transitioning into the role of: "${role}".

Write the plan from the perspective of an elite, no-nonsense operator who has successfully built this path multiple times. Follow these constraints strictly:

1. Act as a brutal realist—do not give fluffy motivation. Focus only on high-execution tactical moves.
2. Outline the exact sequence of the first 3 critical projects that must be shipped to build visible proof of competence.
3. Define 1 daily micro-habit that acts as a lead indicator of success for a "${role}".
4. Give a "Reverse-Fear Warning": Identify the single most common mistake beginners make in this role and how to preempt it.
5. Provide a 4-week structured calendar breakdown showing exactly how to distribute focus.`;

      promptTextArea.value = prompt;
      outputContainer.style.display = 'block';
      outputContainer.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
    }

    function copyHackPrompt() {
      const promptText = document.getElementById('hack-prompt-text');
      promptText.select();
      promptText.setSelectionRange(0, 99999);
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(promptText.value);

      // Show toast
      const t = document.getElementById('toast');
      t.innerText = 'Engineered Prompt Copied!';
      t.style.display = 'block';
      setTimeout(() => t.style.display = 'none', 2500);
    }

    function toast() {
      let t = document.getElementById('toast');
      t.innerText = 'Your NextSelf moment is ready to share.';
      t.style.display = 'block';
      setTimeout(() => t.style.display = 'none', 2500);
    }

    // Setup scroll reveal animation
    const revealElements = document.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(entries => {
      entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('show');
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });

    revealElements.forEach(el => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
</body>

</html>